---
title: Cal Smart Caper-Dill Dressed Double Salmon with Couscous, Tomatoes and Spinach
description: Capers add a briny pop to this salmon dish with creamy Dijon-dill sauce! Underneath, there's a bed of lemony couscous to soak up all those delicious flavours.

